d 9 hours for graduate students). Important Scholarship Facts: A scholarship of $1,000 will waive out-of state tuition for international students and out-of-state students for the academic year. Failure to fulfill scholarship requirements will result in revocation of scholarship funds. Eligible recipients may be supported no longer than 4 years for BS degree or 2 years for MS degree. The submission of a scholarship application does not automatically guarantee a scholarship. The awards are competitive and based on availability of funds. Financial Aid CLICK HERE to apply for UNT scholarship Contact Us: College of Merchandising, Hospitality & Tourism 1155 Union Circle, #311100 Denton, TX 76203-5017 USA Voice: 940-565-2436 Fax: 940.565.4348 Visit Us: Chilton Hall Room Number: 331, 410 S. Avenue C Denton, TX 76201 http://cmht.unt.edu/ Email us: Have questions on content? Please contact us. cmht@unt.edu Technical problems: Have questions concerning how the site runs? Sampath.Pamidimukkala@unt.edu UNT System: UNT Home UNT System UNT Dallas UNT Health Science Center Site last updated on May 1, 2017 Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy Statement | Web Accessibility Policy | State of Texas Online | Emergency Preparedness 